    h2 #[strong Synerg'hetic]
    p.
      Synerg'hetic is one the best four French Junior-Enterprises since 2017. It's a student association.
      For one year I was Synerg'hetic's Vice-treasurer and Web Developer, and was part of a team of eleven students in charge of managing our Junior-Enterprise.
    p.
      Synerg'hetic in a few numbers:#[br]
      - 150.000 € in turnover every year #[br]
      - 325 different clients in 13 years #[br]
      - 117 alumni #[br]
      - 40% of clients are entrepreneurs or debuting startups

    p The Junior-Entreprises movement is the biggest student movement in France, with 180 associations.

    img(src="/images/synergfamily.jpg", alt="Synerg'hetic's 2017/18 team", data-action="zoom")

